               <p>Q. You keep the house to which these articles were removed - A. I do; I occupy the whole house. 
               <persName id="t18140420-56-person562">
                  Susannah 
                  Brazely
               <interp inst="t18140420-56-person562" type="surname" value="Brazely"></interp>
