                     <interp inst="t18140420-56-person567" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , he had suspicion he had a hat of his. I went to the house where he lodged, No. 8, Windmill-street, with Mr. Bartrop, Mr. Ingram, and Mr. Harris. I opened the box, and took the piece of Irish linen out. I left the piece of linen at Hatton Garden office, in Read's possession.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18140420-56-person568">
                  THOMAS 
                  PICKERING
               <interp inst="t18140420-56-person568" type="surname" value="PICKERING"></interp>
