            . I am a servant to Mr. Harris; I was so at the time of the fire. I assisted in removing the goods from Mr. Bartrop's to master; what goods I took I put in the parlour. I knew both the prisoners. 
               <persName id="t18140420-56-person569">
                  Edward 
                  Brazely
               <interp inst="t18140420-56-person569" type="surname" value="Brazely"></interp>
